quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,105,My sent nadol ona scripture truthfully v poradie do judge among the ludia v accordance s co GOD shown ona! Ona nie strana betrayers
  4,106,Ona implore GOD forgiveness. GOD bol Forgiver Merciful
  4,107,Nie argue on behalf z those zlo ich own souls; GOD nie laska any betrayer guilty
  4,108,They zatajit ludia nie care zatajit GOD He je them mat rad they harbor idea He nemat rad! GOD JE fully aware z everything they ROBIT
  4,109,Tu ty bol arguing ich behalf v this world argue GOD ich behalf Dni Vzkriesenie? Kto bol ich zastanca
  4,110,Ktokolvek commits zly zlo jeho soul potom implores GOD forgiveness zalozit GOD Forgiving Merciful
  4,111,Ktokolvek zarabat zhresit zarabat it detriment jeho own soul. GOD bol Omniscient Wise
  4,112,Ktokolvek zarabat zhresit potom zalovat innocent clovek thereof committed blasphemy gross offense